casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Dennis Keith TOWNE, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157210
COA: 322820 Supreme Court of Michigan. April 26, 2019

Order

By order of the Chief Justice, the motion of defendant-appellant to extend the time for filing his supplemental brief is GRANTED. The supplemental brief will be accepted as timely filed if submitted on or before June 7, 2019.
